author: Ubisoft
description:
The wind rises again on Fortress. Watch the Season 4 Reveal on November 16, live on Twitch and YouTube, to learn more about the map rework.

About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6SiegeX

author: Ubisoft
description:
The Rogue Prince of Persia launches on Nintendo Switch™ and Nintendo Switch™ 2 on December 16, 2025.

Platform in a shifting kingdom and master an acrobatic combat style in this fast-paced 2D action roguelite imagined by Evil Empire.

Be ready to Rewrite Fate, Save Persia... Or Die Trying.

The Rogue Prince of Persia is a challenging, fast-paced roguelite, where every death is a unique chance to rewrite fate, save Persia – or die trying. Explore and platform in a shifting kingdom imagined by Evil Empire, master an acrobatic combat style, and meet new allies as you fight to rewrite the fate of your people.

author: Ubisoft
description:
The devs have a message for you: REGIONAL BETA 3 starts in a few days, watch the briefing to get all the details and the latest news regarding the Division Resurgence.

Pre-register now to unlock unique rewards at launch! https://www.thedivisionresurgence.com/

The Division Resurgence is a free-to-play third-person shooter RPG set in a shared MMO open-world. It takes place in a contemporary post-crisis New-York city, after a virus outbreak has created chaos and the collapse of the American government. 

 In this whole new spectacular experience of the Division creatively crafted for mobile, you embody an agent of the « Strategic Homeland Division » and your mission is to restore order, combat hostile factions, protect civilians and help them build a better future.

title: The Division Resurgence: [NEW REGIONAL BETA!]
